properties.areaDesc: James River from Jamestown to the James River Bridge; James River from James River Bridge to Hampton Roads Bridge-Tunnel
properties.headline: Dense Fog Advisory issued January 14 at 6:29PM EST until January 15 at 7:00AM EST by NWS Wakefield VA
properties.description:
* WHAT...Dense fog will reduce visibilities below 1 NM at times
through tonight.

* WHERE...James River from Jamestown to the James River Bridge
and James River from James River Bridge to Hampton Roads
Bridge- Tunnel.

* WHEN...Until 7 AM EST Wednesday.

* IMPACTS...Low visibility will make navigation difficult.
properties.instruction:
If you must navigate, proceed with caution. Use proper fog
signals. Make sure all running lights are on. Remember to use
your radar and compass.

NWSheadline: DENSE FOG ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 7 AM EST WEDNESDAY
